Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.73,0:00:02.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Filling in the distance between hate and love...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.56,0:00:04.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The deductions and the suspense of two people!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.35,0:00:05.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A difficult case in search of the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.81,0:00:07.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A courtroom clash between Kisaki and the prosecution!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.94,0:00:09.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Perceiving the one and only truth...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.48,0:00:11.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The appearance of a child and the intellect of an adult...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.28,0:00:13.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His name is: Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.60,0:01:44.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,An onsen, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.97,0:01:47.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We haven't been to one in so long, have we?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.73,0:01:51.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And it's fall leaf-viewing season now, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.11,0:01:52.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.19,0:01:57.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I recommend this open-air bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.07,0:01:59.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They say this onsen is really good for the body!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.20,0:02:04.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mom, you have to take a break from work once in a while and just relax.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.08,0:02:06.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.16,0:02:08.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kuriyama{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.41,0:02:11.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What does my schedule look like for next month?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.54,0:02:17.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The current court case is scheduled to be resolved next week, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.26,0:02:19.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's left depends on what you decide as far as the issue of the duty roster...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.05,0:02:21.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.05,0:02:21.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There was that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.43,0:02:24.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you would bring the documents for that...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.14,0:02:24.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.35,0:02:28.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's a duty roster?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.10,0:02:36.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sometimes there are defendants who cannot employ the services of a lawyer due to financial reasons and such.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.73,0:02:41.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's when the government appoints an attorney, but when none of us wants the case, it's left to the duty roster.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.95,0:02:44.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.62,0:02:49.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've only given the case a quick glance-over, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.58,0:02:52.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wonder why no one chose to take it on?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.83,0:02:55.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It looks like the defendant has a decent case here...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.38,0:02:59.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wonder if it's because the opponent is unfavorable?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.05,0:02:59.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The opponent?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.38,0:03:03.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The one heading this case is Prosecutor Kujou.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.10,0:03:08.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.89,0:03:10.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The Madonna of Prosecutors, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.52,0:03:18.23,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,COURTROOM CONFRONTATION II: KISAKI VS KUJOU\N(PART ONE)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.69,0:03:19.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.99,0:03:22.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Should we say we're occupied and refuse it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.99,0:03:26.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Say, Kisaki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sensei{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.87,0:03:28.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What kind of a case is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.62,0:03:32.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's something that occurred about a month ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.21,0:03:36.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The body of a company's president was found in his office in Haido City.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.75,0:03:41.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,From the fingerprints and the articles left inside the room...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.01,0:03:44.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They were able to apprehend the defendant—a habitual offender that had broken into many establishments.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.01,0:03:48.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It doesn't seem like a case that would end up in court...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.68,0:03:51.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's true...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.23,0:03:54.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since the defendant had already admitted to breaking in, being discovered by the victim...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.73,0:03:58.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And against his better judgment, hitting the victim in the head with the ashtray during the struggle.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.23,0:04:01.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,he problem is with the charge listed on the indictment.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.03,0:04:03.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The charge?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.70,0:04:07.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,On the indictment, it is charged as a robbery-murder.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.37,0:04:08.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Murder?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.83,0:04:11.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But in that case, wouldn't it be an accidental death?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.37,0:04:13.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.62,0:04:18.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I find it hard to imagine Prosecutor Kujou would have made such a mistake, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.71,0:04:20.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kuriyama{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.01,0:04:23.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I already have the prosecutorial and fact-falsehood memos, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.42,0:04:26.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I still lack the conditional examination papers—could you get them for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.84,0:04:29.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll also need a copy of the autopsy report.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.60,0:04:31.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.73,0:04:34.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Ran.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.14,0:04:37.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Due to this, the onsen will have to wait for another time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.98,0:04:42.61,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Tokyo Detention Center
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.99,0:04:44.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let me confirm once more with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.03,0:04:46.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,On the night of the incident...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.99,0:04:50.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You broke the window to the Ootsu Real Estate Company's office on the second floor of the Nomoto Building...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.99,0:04:50.49,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Inoue Takashi (55)\NSuspect
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.49,0:04:51.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And proceeded to enter the office.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.45,0:04:57.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,While you were searching around the office, and trying to open the safe in the company president's office...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.83,0:05:03.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You were discovered by the company's president, Ootsu Toshiyuki, when he returned for business purposes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.76,0:05:10.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, during the struggle, you used the glass ashtray to strike him in the head.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.35,0:05:16.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All this resulting in death.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.48,0:05:17.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is all correct, yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.65,0:05:19.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.06,0:05:22.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What happened to the money in the safe?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.82,0:05:24.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.11,0:05:26.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,However, according to testimony from the company employees...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.65,0:05:31.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The 12,000,000 yen in cash taken in that day from a real estate transaction had disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.16,0:05:37.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The prosecution believes that, after you killed President Ootsu, you opened the safe and stole the money.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.25,0:05:39.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It wasn't me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.42,0:05:40.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I really don't know anything about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.29,0:05:44.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's certainly true that the money wasn't found in your room, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.80,0:05:51.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Given that your fingerprints were found on the dial of the safe, the prosecution's suspicions aren't entirely baseless.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.26,0:05:53.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I really didn't take the money...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.35,0:05:54.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And about that person...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.72,0:05:55.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That person?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.39,0:05:58.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you know the victim beforehand?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.11,0:06:10.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How many times did you strike the victim's head?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.82,0:06:12.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dunno.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.28,0:06:13.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Was it one time?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.45,0:06:15.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Two times?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.04,0:06:16.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.54,0:06:19.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After all, I was surprised and discovered unexpectedly.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.46,0:06:25.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,According to the autopsy, there are traces of the victim having been struck three times.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.59,0:06:28.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And it was the third that proved to be the fatal blow.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.01,0:06:31.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If it were a single time, it'd be best.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.84,0:06:36.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But with two or three times, the possibility exists that you would be regarded as having intended to kill him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.60,0:06:38.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I really don't remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.02,0:06:40.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.35,0:06:46.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I am your ally, so even if it's unfavorable towards your case, please tell me everything honestly.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.07,0:06:50.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let me confirm once more.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.99,0:06:54.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You really didn't intend to kill the victim, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.78,0:06:56.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.49,0:06:57.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.58,0:07:00.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In court, we shall press that one point in our argument.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.54,0:07:02.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.00,0:07:06.25,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Tokyo District Court
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.00,0:07:08.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The defendant Inoue Takashi, at approximately 20:30 hours on the night of the incident...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.42,0:07:11.26,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,The Case of the Robbery-Murder of the Real Estate Company President\NFirst Public Hearing
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.42,0:07:12.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,On the second floor of the Nomoto Building in Haido City Block 3-2-9...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.68,0:07:14.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Broke the window of the Ootsu Real Estate president's office and trespassed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.43,0:07:18.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,While searching for money and other goods...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.10,0:07:25.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was discovered by that company's president, Ootsu Toshiyuki, who had returned to attend to business matters.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.90,0:07:28.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Using a weapon in his possession...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.82,0:07:31.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He threatened that same person to open the door of the safe in the room...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.90,0:07:35.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And utilizing a glass ashtray that was also in the room, struck the victim's head three times until he was dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.78,0:07:41.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He then stole the 12,000,000 yen deposited in the safe, and escaped.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.50,0:07:46.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Therefore, we request that the defendant be charged under Article 240 of the Penal Code, Robbery-Murder...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.38,0:07:49.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And sentenced to life in prison with hard labor.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.30,0:07:54.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Does the defendant admit to the prosecution's accusation?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.97,0:07:56.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Or do you deny it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.56,0:08:00.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I only entered to steal...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.52,0:08:02.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As far as intention to kill...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.14,0:08:02.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your Honor!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.69,0:08:04.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Proceed, counselor.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.65,0:08:08.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The accusation is robbery-murder...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.82,0:08:10.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But the defendant did not intend to murder the victim.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.61,0:08:12.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Therefore I would like to raise an objection.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.36,0:08:15.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So he denies the charge of robbery-murder?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.91,0:08:22.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I believe it would be more appropriate to change the charge from Article 240 to Article 205, Assault Leading to Death.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.25,0:08:27.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The defense appears to have an objection with the prosecution's accusation.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.38,0:08:28.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you have any concerns?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.84,0:08:30.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, just one.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.42,0:08:34.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The reason the defendant chose Ootsu Real Estate...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.30,0:08:35.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.26,0:08:40.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was just that while I was looking for a building to enter and steal from...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.10,0:08:41.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I happened to come across that building by chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.48,0:08:43.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If that's the case...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.73,0:08:46.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was just a coincidence that you chose to steal from Ootsu Real Estate...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.35,0:08:50.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And you contend you had no existing grudge whatsoever against the victim Ootsu Toshiyuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.61,0:08:52.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is all of this correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.32,0:08:53.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.32,0:08:57.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wonder what Prosecutor Kujou is trying to say...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.12,0:08:59.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your Honor!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.12,0:09:01.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The prosecution's aim with this line of questioning is unclear!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.70,0:09:03.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well then.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.12,0:09:07.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The defendant is familiar with a female by the name of Endou Noriko, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.50,0:09:10.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.09,0:09:14.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's no reason you would forget your only daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.76,0:09:16.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Only daughter?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.68,0:09:18.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.01,0:09:23.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She was only eight years old when he divorced his ex-wife twenty years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.52,0:09:26.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I wonder what that has to do with this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.48,0:09:29.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is it that you can't answer?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.40,0:09:30.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Objection!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.19,0:09:38.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The prosecution only seeks to put the defendant at unease by bringing up the name of a blood relative!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.87,0:09:43.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that daughter relevant to the court in any way?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.83,0:09:44.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.95,0:09:50.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Endou Noriko runs a snack stand in another building that Ootsu Real Estate manages.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.59,0:09:54.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It has been rumored that she was involved with the victim, Ootsu Toshiyuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.80,0:10:01.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're saying it was not by coincidence the defendant broke into the building that became the crime scene?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.60,0:10:02.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.06,0:10:07.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We also have testimony to the effect that the defendant held a grudge against the victim because of his daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.77,0:10:08.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.94,0:10:11.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't know anything about that!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.48,0:10:13.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If that's the case, shall we ask the person in question?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.48,0:10:16.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since she is in the visitor's gallery, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.94,0:10:19.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We can have her come out here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.78,0:10:24.45,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Endou Noriko (28)\NInoue Takashi's Daughter
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.37,0:10:24.45,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Daddy...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.04,0:10:27.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Noriko...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.71,0:10:32.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So this is the card the Madonna had hidden up her sleeve?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.17,0:10:38.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If it's necessary, we are prepared to have Endou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} testify as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.69,0:10:55.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So it's true what the prosecutor said?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.52,0:10:56.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.57,0:10:59.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was deceived by that man.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.90,0:11:04.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He said sweet things such as how he would allow me to keep the shop, and took terrible advantage of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.58,0:11:07.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When did you get into contact with your father?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.70,0:11:11.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I reunited with him nearly two years ago when my mother passed away from illness.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.62,0:11:15.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ever since, he would occasionally stop by my shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.21,0:11:18.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And you told him about Ootsu{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} then?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.88,0:11:23.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He said he'd get consolation money out of him for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.72,0:11:27.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, it's certainly turned into an unfavorable situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.97,0:11:28.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.97,0:11:33.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because, if he held a grudge against the other party and hit him as many as three times...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.56,0:11:37.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No one would believe him even if he said he didn't intend to kill the victim.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.73,0:11:38.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.03,0:11:41.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Lastly, I'd like for you to answer me truthfully...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.36,0:11:46.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you also think your father murdered Ootsu Toshiyuki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.91,0:11:52.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, Daddy likes stealing, but he's not someone who would kill a person!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.96,0:11:53.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.08,0:11:58.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It looks like the battle to come will be an intense one this time...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.60,0:12:14.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Geez, Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.27,0:12:17.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dozing off again!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.19,0:12:21.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was just resting my eyes while thinking!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.69,0:12:23.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who's dozing off?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.66,0:12:25.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, have you hit upon it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.53,0:12:29.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A good idea you can use to help Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.04,0:12:31.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.29,0:12:36.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Taking on this sort of case, it's Eri's own fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.29,0:12:43.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The defendant had a motive to murder, and on top of that his fingerprints were clearly on the dial of the safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.76,0:12:46.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How is somebody supposed to defend against that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.76,0:12:51.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I wonder why the dial on the safe was the only place his fingerprints were found?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.60,0:12:54.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As for that, he probably snuck in wearing gloves!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.44,0:13:00.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, since gloves get in the way when it comes to precise tasks such as turning the dial on a safe, he removed them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.32,0:13:03.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's when the victim came in, and so using the ashtray...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.07,0:13:07.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If that's the case, his fingerprints should also be on the ashtray since it was the weapon, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.16,0:13:08.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.95,0:13:10.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since he'd taken his gloves off.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.41,0:13:14.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But there were no fingerprints left on the ashtray.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.83,0:13:18.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, of course he wiped his fingerprints off afterward!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.00,0:13:18.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let me see that!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.54,0:13:22.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Read this part carefully!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.67,0:13:27.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't it written here that there are traces of it having been wiped down with an oil-stained cloth?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.68,0:13:31.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If that's so, why didn't he wipe down the safe as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.51,0:13:32.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, that's because...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.85,0:13:37.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He accidentally killed someone, so in his haste, he fled and forgot about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.27,0:13:38.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.81,0:13:42.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I wonder when he stole the money from the safe?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.19,0:13:45.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, after he committed the murder, he opened the safe again, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.49,0:13:48.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Didn't you just say he fled in haste?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.70,0:13:49.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.82,0:13:52.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Somehow, it seems mismatched, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.70,0:13:53.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.87,0:13:57.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Criminals do all kinds of things that don't make sense!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.12,0:14:00.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't that just a sophism?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.21,0:14:00.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.96,0:14:02.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm getting out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.30,0:14:05.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait, Dad, where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.84,0:14:10.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Geez...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.76,0:14:16.31,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,List of Articles Found at the Crime Scene\N1. Glass Ashtray\N2. 1 Pair of Army Cotton Gloves\N3. Eyeglasses screw\N4. Golf Ball
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.54,0:14:36.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, Dear!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.66,0:14:37.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.25,0:14:40.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.25,0:14:42.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, just something...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.50,0:14:47.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You came to the scene of the crime to see if there was anything you could do to help Kisaki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sensei{\r}, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.72,0:14:48.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.47,0:14:49.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.13,0:14:52.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mr. Great Detective sure has a lot of free time, doesn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.89,0:14:53.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's that!?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.18,0:14:56.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kisaki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sensei{\r}, you came to investigate the crime scene as well, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.18,0:14:58.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.10,0:15:01.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm getting permission from the building manager right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.06,0:15:06.82,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Akiyama Takuya (56) Building Manager
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.06,0:15:05.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you for waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.52,0:15:06.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This way, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.61,0:15:12.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mister, you were the first person to discover the company president?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.12,0:15:14.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right, my boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.58,0:15:17.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could we hear a detailed account of what happened at that time?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.75,0:15:18.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.79,0:15:24.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,On that night, at around 9:00, I was watching a baseball game on TV when...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.80,0:15:29.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Arima{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.92,0:15:33.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Have you seen Dad—no, I mean, Mr. President?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.05,0:15:37.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When I made my rounds at 8:00, no one was in the office...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.06,0:15:39.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.27,0:15:43.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When he left my restaurant a bit ago, he said he was coming back to the office.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.60,0:15:46.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In that case, he must've come in through one of the emergency exits.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.40,0:15:51.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, the door to the office is locked, and there was no answer even though I called for him many times.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.95,0:15:54.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wouldn't he be in the rear office?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.99,0:15:57.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I came to drop off the reading glasses he left behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.83,0:16:01.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry, but could you come and open the door for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.00,0:16:01.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.12,0:16:08.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The Arima{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} you mentioned was President Ootsu's adopted son-in-law, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.55,0:16:09.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.38,0:16:12.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He runs a nearby Italian restaurant.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.59,0:16:16.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So it was this door that was locked, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.35,0:16:19.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I used this spare key to open the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.07,0:16:31.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It sure doesn't look like he's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.15,0:16:36.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dad, you there?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.24,0:16:38.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's me, Masahiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.20,0:16:40.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.16,0:16:41.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.83,0:16:42.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's someone there!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.04,0:16:48.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.42,0:16:50.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.75,0:16:53.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Someone inside is being beaten!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.09,0:16:53.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What'd you say!?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.68,0:16:56.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The key for the door!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.80,0:16:59.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The company president is the only one with the key to this door!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.26,0:17:00.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Damn...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.26,0:17:01.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Move aside please!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.10,0:17:06.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.69,0:17:08.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hang in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.86,0:17:09.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.36,0:17:12.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Akiyama{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, please hurry and call an ambulance!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.78,0:17:13.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.87,0:17:23.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The company president's office is over there, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.54,0:17:29.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, this door is locked.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.63,0:17:32.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Arima{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} is in possession of the key to this room.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.88,0:17:34.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.84,0:17:36.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Arima{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.01,0:17:40.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is Kisaki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, the attorney I mentioned on the phone and...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.22,0:17:42.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm Detective Mouri Kogorou.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.62,0:17:46.06,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Arima Masahiko (35)\NProprietor of an Italian Restaurant
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.14,0:17:44.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're the famous...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.10,0:17:46.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.77,0:17:49.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Arima{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, apologies for interrupting your work.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.65,0:17:52.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We were wondering if you would let us take a look in the company president's office.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.15,0:17:56.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Say, is this room not being used right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.03,0:18:00.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even though the police have already completed their investigation...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.28,0:18:03.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since it was the room in which Dad died under such circumstances...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.83,0:18:06.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's hard to say what we'll do with it from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.25,0:18:08.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.29,0:18:11.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's just as the police left it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.00,0:18:11.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.43,0:18:26.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, Arima{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.18,0:18:28.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where was it that the victim fell?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.23,0:18:30.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.69,0:18:32.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was right around here, in front of the safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.69,0:18:35.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was on the floor, cradling his head in his arms.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.61,0:18:36.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.49,0:18:38.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So that's how it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.91,0:18:41.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"That's how it was"?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.62,0:18:46.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Most likely, Inoue was discovered by the victim as he was trying to open the safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.70,0:18:49.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The defendant had already stated as much.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.29,0:18:50.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's important is what happened afterward.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.96,0:18:57.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inoue used a knife or something he had hidden on him to threaten the victim into opening the safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.97,0:19:01.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And then, when it was opened, he used the ashtray, and from behind...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.18,0:19:03.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Struck him down.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.26,0:19:07.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're not saying the defendant is lying, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.47,0:19:10.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, if he wanted you believe that he was innocent, that's probably it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.52,0:19:13.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's no way to defend a defendant if you don't believe him, is there?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.90,0:19:19.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can say all the neat phrases you want, but you're only going to get thrashed by that Madonna!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.08,0:19:30.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Say Mister, where you saw the culprit from...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.41,0:19:31.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Was it this tiny window?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.42,0:19:33.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.38,0:19:34.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.09,0:19:42.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Conan.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.22,0:19:43.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just what are you up to?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.39,0:19:47.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uncle Kogorou, could you stand in front of the safe again for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.39,0:19:49.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Geez...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.47,0:19:50.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is this about?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.44,0:19:54.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Around here?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.86,0:19:56.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just wait there for a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.82,0:19:59.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.28,0:20:02.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah-le!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.11,0:20:06.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,From here, Uncle is hidden by the screen and I can't see him at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.12,0:20:08.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What'd you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.62,0:20:09.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Akiyama{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.62,0:20:10.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's the meaning of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.91,0:20:12.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.12,0:20:14.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What I saw wasn't over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.79,0:20:17.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was just the shadow of a person I saw reflected over on this wall.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.71,0:20:20.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A shadow reflected on the wall?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.67,0:20:21.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.55,0:20:24.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At that time, the lights in the room were off...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.22,0:20:29.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And I saw the culprit's shadow reflected by the neon lights shining in from the window.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.27,0:20:34.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The shadow of someone hitting Ootsu{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} over and over.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.02,0:20:40.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And after that, I also heard the sound of Ootsu{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} falling to the ground, so there's no mistake!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.36,0:20:42.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm going to ask you one more time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.86,0:20:47.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You did not, then, see Defendant Inoue actually striking the victim, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.53,0:20:48.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, Miss Attorney...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.24,0:20:51.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's not an important difference, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.87,0:20:54.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The culprit even said that he struck him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.33,0:20:55.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, Arima{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.83,0:20:58.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Merely seeing a shadow of someone striking another...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.54,0:21:01.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is completely different from seeing the actual person striking him.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.71,0:21:05.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No matter the circumstances, until the defendant is tried and a guilty verdict comes down in court...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.80,0:21:09.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He is still considered a defendant, and not a culprit.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.72,0:21:13.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When such sad feelings are involved, everyone tends to confuse the two.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.02,0:21:16.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.10,0:21:16.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Say, Mister.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.48,0:21:20.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This clock's stopped, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.40,0:21:26.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was a prize that the late company president won in a golf tournament.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.07,0:21:30.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was placed there as a commemoration ornament, and isn't usually used.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.95,0:21:34.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Arima{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, if you could come over here a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.16,0:21:34.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.75,0:21:35.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.25,0:21:38.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The combination to the safe in question...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.33,0:21:42.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did anyone else know it outside the victim?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.59,0:21:44.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, only my father knew.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.55,0:21:46.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,For security reasons...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.88,0:21:49.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He didn't even tell the accounting heads.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.89,0:21:52.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're in the way, just loitering around!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.27,0:21:55.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.02,0:21:59.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see, I understand it now...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.44,0:22:00.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The trick behind this case!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.98,0:22:05.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The shadow of someone beating someone else that Akiyama{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} supposedly saw...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.28,0:22:08.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And the sound of something having fallen...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.03,0:22:11.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Using this trick, it could all be manufactured!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.20,0:22:14.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And the one who set this trick up...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.54,0:22:16.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Gould only be that person!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.38,0:22:28.09,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,COURTROOM CONFRONTATION II: KISAKI VS KUJOU\N(PART TWO)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.18,0:22:32.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much for your assistance.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.14,0:22:33.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.01,0:22:36.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you find anything that'll help you in the trial?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.01,0:22:36.31,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Arima Masahiko (35)\NProprietor of an Italian Restaurant
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.56,0:22:41.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, since the police and the prosecution have already investigated everything thoroughly...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.65,0:22:45.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's not like we could have found out anything new.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.69,0:22:46.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.24,0:22:47.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, right!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.53,0:22:52.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How about having dinner at my restaurant?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.91,0:22:54.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll bring out my best wine!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.29,0:22:56.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, no thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.79,0:23:00.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since he's offering, let's give it a try!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.62,0:23:01.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dear...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.17,0:23:04.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't Ran waiting at home?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.46,0:23:06.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your daughter?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.13,0:23:10.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If that's the case, she is welcome as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.59,0:23:12.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry to trouble you!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.80,0:23:13.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.68,0:23:16.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Meals taste better when eaten as a group, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.81,0:23:18.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then we shall accept.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.49,0:23:32.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This wine is quite magnificent!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.20,0:23:34.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm honored that you find it to your liking.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.62,0:23:37.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The atmosphere of your restaurant is also lovely.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.16,0:23:39.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.46,0:23:44.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've also been called to appear in the next hearing as a witness.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.50,0:23:46.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please go easy on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.05,0:23:51.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I believe you discovered your father when you went to deliver something he left behind, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.51,0:23:55.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He had left his glasses behind after having taken his meal here.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.93,0:23:57.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Glasses?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.01,0:23:58.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Reading glasses.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.93,0:24:02.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well then, please take your time and enjoy your meal.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.11,0:24:12.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Somehow, the pasta doesn't seem quite up to the standards of a fine restaurant, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.82,0:24:13.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Seems so.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.91,0:24:16.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's a little too much olive oil.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.04,0:24:21.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Anyway, how is it going?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.41,0:24:23.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Have you thought up a strategy for the next hearing?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.46,0:24:25.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's pretty difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.75,0:24:28.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's impossible unless you change the legal system.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.75,0:24:31.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do you mean by that?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.42,0:24:34.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's impossible to overturn it from being a robbery-murder.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.68,0:24:37.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His daughter can already confirm that, because of his feelings as a parent...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.51,0:24:41.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He had a reason to hold a grudge towards the victim.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.10,0:24:44.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So you're saying to confirm the prosecution's version of events...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.73,0:24:47.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And try for a lesser sentence due to the extenuating circumstances?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.44,0:24:49.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's probably no other way.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.11,0:24:50.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This isn't a joke!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.57,0:24:52.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The defendant says that he had no intention to murder the victim.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.20,0:24:56.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You'll get trounced by the Madonna exactly because you're still being taken in by that!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.82,0:24:59.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't remember you ever having gone into a courtroom battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.91,0:25:03.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't know why I ever wanted to help you in the first place!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.17,0:25:07.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come on, stop it you two...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.33,0:25:09.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How did we come to this?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.63,0:25:12.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If I remember correctly, in the list of articles left at the scene...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.05,0:25:17.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It should be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.64,0:25:21.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I found it!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.14,0:25:23.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The decisive evidence!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.23,0:25:25.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.10,0:25:26.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.31,0:25:28.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Looking at the court documents...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.86,0:25:32.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There was just something that bothered me...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.11,0:25:33.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Something that bothered you?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.78,0:25:37.49,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,List of Articles Found at the Crime Scene\N1. Glass Ashtray\N2. 1 Pair of Army Cotton Gloves\N3. Eyeglasses screw\N4. Golf Ball
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.78,0:25:36.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,See, in this list of articles left at the scene of the crime...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.78,0:25:37.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Give me that!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.07,0:25:41.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Once again you're going through important documents without permission!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.50,0:25:44.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Geez.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.83,0:25:49.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you're going to be like that, you'd better come up with something to help Mom out!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.88,0:25:54.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't even care if that stubborn woman gets beaten to a pulp by the Madonna!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.30,0:25:59.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're saying that, but you really don't have any confidence you can win against that Madonna, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.64,0:26:00.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.89,0:26:03.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That kind of little girl, I could take on two of them at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.27,0:26:05.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If that's the case, how about if you become the defense attorney, Uncle?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.10,0:26:07.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's not possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.10,0:26:09.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dad doesn't have the qualifications to become a defense attorney.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.85,0:26:12.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But if he were to become a special counsel, it'd be all right, wouldn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.94,0:26:13.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.19,0:26:17.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a policy in which, as long as it is at the request of the defendant...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.36,0:26:22.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,h person who only possesses ordinary qualifications can represent them in court.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.37,0:26:27.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let the people at the court hear one of your great deductions, Uncle!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.37,0:26:31.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,One of my great deductions, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.75,0:26:35.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No matter how hard the case, in my hands...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.51,0:26:41.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If it's insisted upon, I guess I'd think about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.93,0:26:46.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That person is going to become a special counsel?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.14,0:26:48.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.02,0:26:50.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He said that he absolutely wants to be of assistance to you, Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.40,0:26:53.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thanks, but no thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.86,0:26:54.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.82,0:26:57.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's so rare that Dad gets this kind of idea...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.82,0:27:01.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even so, I can't think of any way that person could be helpful.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.37,0:27:03.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.49,0:27:11.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I have a message from Uncle, for Kisaki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sensei{\r} to go to the crime scene tonight, with the building manager.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.88,0:27:13.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To that building?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.00,0:27:17.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He said you'd be able to see something that would influence the direction of the trial!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.42,0:27:20.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The direction of the trial?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.51,0:27:24.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry for all the trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.26,0:27:26.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't really mind, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.35,0:27:28.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just what do you want with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.39,0:27:31.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, even I don't know exactly...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.40,0:27:35.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mr. Building Manager...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.27,0:27:38.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could you once again do what you did on the night of the incident?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.74,0:27:40.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.03,0:27:42.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where is our man?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.62,0:27:45.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's just outside, making preparations.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.24,0:27:48.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Got it, got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.79,0:27:50.08,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Akiyama Takuya (56) Building Manager
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.83,0:27:50.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do the same thing again, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.79,0:27:55.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let me see, on that night we came into this office and no one was here, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.54,0:27:59.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Arima{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} peeked into the company president's office through this small window...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.38,0:28:01.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And said, "There's someone there," right?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.68,0:28:02.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.84,0:28:05.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And then when I peeked in...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.68,0:28:07.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.43,0:28:09.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could it be...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.18,0:28:11.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.56,0:28:13.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is someone inside?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.10,0:28:14.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why in the world...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.35,0:28:17.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kisaki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sensei{\r}, why don't you confirm it with your own eyes?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.82,0:28:20.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.86,0:28:24.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I recreated the trick like Uncle told me to.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.95,0:28:26.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Trick?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.95,0:28:28.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, could it be that the culprit is...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.12,0:28:33.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uncle said he'd explain everything in detail at the trial.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.04,0:28:38.67,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,The Case of the Robbery-Murder of the Real Estate Company President\NSecond Public Hearing
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.26,0:28:47.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If Mom and Dad are joining hands, there's nothing to fear, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.14,0:28:52.47,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Inoue Takashi (55)\NSuspect
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.68,0:28:51.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Honestly...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.48,0:28:55.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I never would have expected her to request for Mouri Kogorou as special counsel.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.44,0:28:58.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Counselor Kisaki must be at a total loss.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.82,0:29:00.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All rise!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.41,0:29:16.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Akiyama{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.04,0:29:21.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're testifying that you saw, from the small window in the door to the company president's office...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.05,0:29:23.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The victim was being beaten by the culprit, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.05,0:29:24.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.72,0:29:27.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How many times did the culprit hit the victim?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.01,0:29:31.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,From what I saw, it was three times.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.06,0:29:32.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And right after that...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.56,0:29:36.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You heard the sound of the victim falling to the floor, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.02,0:29:38.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No further questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.23,0:29:41.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Counsel, you may proceed with the cross-examination.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.32,0:29:48.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Akiyama{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.82,0:29:52.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,About your witnessing of the victim being struck...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:52.37,0:29:54.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you see the face of the person doing the striking?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.37,0:30:01.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, I didn't see the person doing the striking directly...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.88,0:30:06.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you didn't see the person directly, what did you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.51,0:30:11.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The culprit's shadow reflected on the wall from the light outside the window.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.06,0:30:15.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Silence!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.39,0:30:19.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What you saw was only the culprit's shadow, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:20.31,0:30:21.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.32,0:30:23.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.73,0:30:26.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even if it was his shadow, as long as.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.95,0:30:29.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,hen, I'll ask you one more time.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.41,0:30:35.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Akiyama{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, was the defendant here the culprit that you saw?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.04,0:30:41.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, the only thing I saw was the shadow of the person doing the striking, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.13,0:30:45.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So you don't know whether the person doing the striking was the defendant or not, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.34,0:30:48.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:51.51,0:30:52.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No further questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.97,0:30:56.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is Dad doing!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.27,0:30:58.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's been sleeping the whole time!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:58.18,0:31:00.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His performance is up next, Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-neechan{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.52,0:31:02.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:03.06,0:31:05.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Moving on, we call witness Arima to the stand.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.61,0:31:08.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Arima{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.78,0:31:13.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Along with the building manager, you heard the sound of the victim falling, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.49,0:31:14.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.24,0:31:15.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's no doubt about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.91,0:31:21.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And then you rammed in the president's locked office door, and plunged into the room.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.88,0:31:23.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.29,0:31:25.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was after the culprit had already fled through the window.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.50,0:31:28.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My father—I mean President Ootsu—was on the floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.09,0:31:32.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What was the condition of the safe at that time?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.59,0:31:34.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was left open.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.26,0:31:36.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No further questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.64,0:31:38.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Go ahead, Counsel.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.77,0:31:45.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All right, I guess it's about time for me to overturn this trial.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.36,0:31:47.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dad, do your best!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.86,0:31:53.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,First, we'll take a look at Uncle's skill.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.38,0:32:13.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All right, special counsel, please begin your questioning.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.93,0:32:14.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.89,0:32:24.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You went to Ootsu Real Estate at about 9:00 at night in order to deliver something the victim left behind, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.06,0:32:24.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.77,0:32:27.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In order to deliver the reading glasses that my father left behind in my shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.77,0:32:31.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,However, the door to the office was locked, and you couldn't go in.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:31.61,0:32:32.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.53,0:32:36.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But really, the door wasn't locked, was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.87,0:32:42.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And the victim was in the company president's office, checking the money in the safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:43.41,0:32:45.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.67,0:32:47.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You don't mean that I...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.38,0:32:52.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, just that you also had the chance to commit the crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.72,0:32:53.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's ridiculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.80,0:32:55.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why would I do that to my father-in-law?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:56.05,0:33:00.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When money is involved, even direct parent-child relationships are pushed to the side.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.39,0:33:04.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Surprisingly, Uncle has struck a good point.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.81,0:33:10.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The question is obviously nothing more than conjecture!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.07,0:33:11.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Objection sustained.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.94,0:33:16.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If the defense could please develop their argument on the basis of clearly defined evidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.53,0:33:17.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.45,0:33:24.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,From my seven years of experience, it happens very often that the first person to discover the body is the culprit.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.87,0:33:27.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, using your seven years of experience...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.00,0:33:31.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How would you explain the articles left at the scene of the crime...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.25,0:33:34.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And the defendant's fingerprints on the dial of the safe?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.22,0:33:39.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When the witness and the victim were arguing over the money...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:39.93,0:33:42.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The defendant took in the situation from outside the window.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.68,0:33:45.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is again unestablished.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.48,0:33:50.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And further, after the witness beat the victim down and left...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.86,0:33:56.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The defendant snuck in and went to steal the money in the safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.32,0:34:01.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If that's the case, then who was this culprit the building manager witnessed?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.99,0:34:05.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In actuality, the victim was not yet dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.58,0:34:09.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And so he regained consciousness, got into a struggle with the defendant...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.34,0:34:17.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If that's the case, then as we were saying, the one who murdered the victim was the defendant, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.09,0:34:20.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I guess that's what it comes down to, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.85,0:34:22.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:22.14,0:34:24.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aren't you here for the sake of defending the defendant?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.93,0:34:29.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I am here as a Great Detective in order to shed light on the truth of this case!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.27,0:34:32.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was a fool to rely on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.44,0:34:34.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:34.73,0:34:35.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Get back here!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.99,0:34:36.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.86,0:34:38.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm still in the middle of this important...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.24,0:34:42.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It would be appreciated if the marital spat could be conducted elsewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.45,0:34:47.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dad sucks!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.04,0:34:50.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I guess that's about as far as Uncle can go.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:51.54,0:34:55.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Anyway, just sit down and shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.46,0:34:56.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What am I, an ornament?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:00.13,0:35:02.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I retract my previous statements.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.47,0:35:03.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your Honor!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.01,0:35:05.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's enough already!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:05.43,0:35:11.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The defendant snuck into that room before Arima{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} entered, not afterwards.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.19,0:35:17.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And, as he was about to open the safe, he was discovered by the victim.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.07,0:35:21.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Without thinking, he struck the victim down and immediately fled.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.86,0:35:23.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The problem is with what happened after that.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:24.45,0:35:32.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The defendant was convinced that he accidentally killed the victim, but in actuality the victim only lost consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.25,0:35:37.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And immediately after that, the victim was murdered by someone who came to the scene of the crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.67,0:35:39.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you saying that's me?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.30,0:35:44.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You testified the victim forgot his reading glasses at your shop, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:46.14,0:35:49.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Does he need his reading glasses even while he's eating?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.77,0:35:52.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Without them, he can't even read the menu.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.98,0:35:55.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't that strange?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.06,0:35:59.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In the indictment, it is written that the victim was forced by the culprit to open the safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.32,0:36:02.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If he didn't have his reading glasses...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:02.49,0:36:06.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wonder how the victim turned the dials on the safe?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.08,0:36:12.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In that dark office in which only the neon signs from the neighboring building were shining.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:12.46,0:36:13.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.29,0:36:15.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I have no idea either.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.59,0:36:20.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wasn't the victim still alive up until you delivered the reading glasses?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.68,0:36:23.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you there?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.47,0:36:26.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.72,0:36:28.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You have a wound on your head!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:28.76,0:36:29.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Leave it!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.68,0:36:30.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:31.35,0:36:33.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was after he had discovered the robber.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.27,0:36:37.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After he regained consciousness, what he should have been the most concerned about was the money.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:37.82,0:36:39.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you're looking for your glasses, here.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:45.57,0:36:47.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When you saw that money...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:48.16,0:36:50.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A murderous urge was born within you...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:51.58,0:36:55.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And you murdered the victim with the toppled ashtray.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:56.79,0:36:57.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Prosecutor!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:57.88,0:37:02.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was called here as a witness, but now I'm being treated as the culprit!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.63,0:37:03.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:03.88,0:37:06.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You have forgotten one important fact.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.97,0:37:09.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That the witness has an alibi for the time of the crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.10,0:37:11.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.10,0:37:13.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,During the time when my father was being struck down and fell...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.64,0:37:15.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was on the outside of the door!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:15.35,0:37:17.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Along with the building manager!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.77,0:37:21.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You probably didn't hear the building manager's testimony.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.78,0:37:25.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He is saying that he didn't see the culprit.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.45,0:37:26.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:26.66,0:37:28.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The shadow of the assailant...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.07,0:37:30.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The shadow reflected on the wall, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:30.99,0:37:34.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After you committed the crime for the sake of money...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.21,0:37:37.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You desperately tried to think of a way to make it seem as if it were the result of a robbery.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:37.50,0:37:39.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's when a certain mechanism came to mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:39.88,0:37:47.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A mechanism using a clock in the president's office that had a decoration attached.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.47,0:37:50.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your Honor.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:52.72,0:37:56.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is a clock in the same shape as the one in the company president's office.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.89,0:38:01.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We believe that the culprit probably set this clock to ring...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:02.53,0:38:05.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And set the doll up so that its movement was reflected on the wall using the light from the window...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.15,0:38:10.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,An optical illusion that lead the building manager to misunderstand the time of the murder.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.49,0:38:12.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And the sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:12.74,0:38:13.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What about the sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:14.25,0:38:17.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The building manager and I, we heard the sound of my father collapsing!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:17.71,0:38:20.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's a simple trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:21.42,0:38:23.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You most likely took a golf ball with a string attached to it...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:23.92,0:38:26.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And put it under the leg of a desk in the company president's office.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:27.76,0:38:31.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Having prepared the end of the string to stick out under the door...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:31.55,0:38:35.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You pulled the string as the building manager was peering in the small window and being taken by surprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:39.44,0:38:42.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How's that for a pretty simple trick?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:44.48,0:38:46.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you have any proof?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:47.70,0:38:48.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That kind of trick...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:48.74,0:38:50.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Anyone could have done it, couldn't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.70,0:38:53.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Show me evidence that I was the one to do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:53.20,0:38:54.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Exactly as the witness said!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.91,0:38:58.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you're going to go as far as to claim that, I would like to see evidence!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:58.96,0:39:00.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As far as evidence, Prosecutor Kujou...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:01.17,0:39:04.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's in the list of articles recovered from the crime scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.09,0:39:06.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In the list?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:08.05,0:39:11.59,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,List of Articles Found at the Crime Scene\N1. Glass Ashtray\N2. 1 Pair of Army Cotton Gloves\N3. Eyeglasses screw\N4. Golf Ball
Dialogue: 0,0:39:08.38,0:39:11.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's an eyeglasses screw in that list, isn't there?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:12.09,0:39:17.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If it's from the victim's reading glasses, I wonder when it fell there.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:18.77,0:39:21.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He should have left his reading glasses at the restaurant, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:23.98,0:39:30.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's no other way to think of it except that it came off when the victim was struck down by the culprit, is there?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:32.74,0:39:34.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Also, Arima{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.49,0:39:39.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You used your work apron to wipe the fingerprints off the ashtray, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:40.50,0:39:46.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,According to the forensic examination of the ashtray, the fingerprints had been wiped down by an oily cloth.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:47.71,0:39:56.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I request a complete analysis comparison of the oil on the ashtray against the olive oil used in Arima's restaurant.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:00.06,0:40:01.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Arima{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:01.27,0:40:06.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After the incident, you repaid a debt of 5,000,000 yen to a money lending company, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.07,0:40:13.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We can recover that money, and examine the fingerprints from it.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.49,0:40:19.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dad deserved it...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:20.12,0:40:21.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That abusive man!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:24.75,0:40:26.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's great, isn't it, Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:26.46,0:40:27.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That the money was untouched...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.63,0:40:29.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you want this money?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.71,0:40:31.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But look here.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:31.92,0:40:35.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you don't return the money I lent you by next week...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:35.09,0:40:38.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll evict you from that shop, even if you are my adopted son-in-law!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:41.43,0:40:43.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's as Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} said.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:43.73,0:40:45.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The one who killed my father was me!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:53.07,0:40:53.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your Honor!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:54.41,0:40:59.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We revise the indictment against Defendant Inoue from Robbery-Murder to Attempted Robbery...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:59.29,0:41:03.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And additionally would like to prepare an accusation against suspect Arima.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:04.04,0:41:06.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How does that sit with the defense?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:06.88,0:41:07.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That is appropriate.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:08.29,0:41:12.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, we conclude the trial for this matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:42.35,0:42:43.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kisaki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:44.39,0:42:47.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,For helping me realize the error of my conclusion...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:47.35,0:42:48.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:49.19,0:42:51.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was merely carrying out my duties.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:52.52,0:42:54.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, see you at the next trial.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:59.53,0:43:02.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Say, in celebration of the conclusion of the trial, why don't we all go out to eat?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:03.70,0:43:05.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now that you mention it, I am hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:06.00,0:43:08.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Delicious wine and Italian food, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:08.83,0:43:11.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe we should go with sake and fresh sashimi!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:11.67,0:43:12.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:12.54,0:43:15.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Cold beer and tempura so hot you'd have to blow at it while you eat it—that'd be great!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:15.92,0:43:19.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Or even Chinese food and old Chinese wine...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:19.72,0:43:21.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Will he ever come to a decision?
